    <strong style="font-size:14px;color:#2E7D32;">How SEO Rules Work</strong>
    <p style="margin:8px 0 0;">
        SEO Rules are evaluated <strong>in real-time</strong> on every frontend page load &mdash; no "Apply" action is needed.
        When a visitor or search engine bot loads a product, category, or CMS page, the rule engine automatically:
    </p>
    <ol style="margin:8px 0 0;padding-left:20px;">
