        <li>Applies the <strong>first matching rule's actions</strong> &mdash; overriding meta title, description, robots directive, or canonical URL</li>
        <li>If <strong>"Stop Processing"</strong> is set to Yes, no further rules are checked after a match</li>
    </ol>
    <p style="margin:8px 0 0;color:#555;">
        <strong>Priority:</strong> Lower number = higher priority. Rules are processed from lowest to highest priority number.
        Results are <strong>cached for 1 hour</strong> for performance. Flush cache to see changes immediately.
